{"tid":2155084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美商會調查53%受訪者考慮離開香港 比例持續增加","createTime":"2020-08-13T13:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T14:00:29.000Z","uid":239336,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9289a79556af459b482b3542a3e0cf4a2c71c87a","tid":2155084,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"美國商會最新調查顯示，在「港版國安法」通過後有多達53％受訪者稱，個人考慮短、中、長期離開香港。美商會指，稱考慮離開香港的比例持續兩個月增加。此外，44％受訪者對香港營商前境感到悲觀，10%受訪者更稱，即使短期樂觀，但對中長期仍感悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n在美國財政部於上周五晚公佈11名中港官員被制裁當日，美國商會由當日起一連5日進行調查，以了解會員對「港版國安法」通過後的看法。自《國安法》通過及更多細節披露後，在受訪的154位會員公司中， 9%受訪者表示考慮短期內離香港，44％受訪者稱考慮中長期離港，表示不會離開香港的則有46％。<br />\n美商會由6月起開始進行同類型調查，表示考慮離開香港的人連續兩個月上升，但商會指，要留意的是，逾8成人也是考慮在中長期離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=b1a2ba16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FLRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=963857b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/LRMTZLAKU5HC5PKSKKURC5MM6Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/